msgstr ""

msgid "During this scenario, investigators will need to use the Moving Platform to navigate the Great Chamber."
msgstr ""

msgid "Locations are not connected to each other except by the Moving Platform or its connecting icons."
msgstr ""

msgid "The Moving Platform is connected to each Location adjacent to it and vice versa"
msgstr ""

