msgstr ""

msgid "When instructed to swap the Moving Platform with an adjacent Chamber Location, simultaneously move each of those Locations (along with all cards and tokens on them) to the space previously occupied by the other."
msgstr ""

msgid "Activating and Deactivating Locations"
msgstr ""

msgid "During this scenario, Locations can be \"activated\" or \"deactivated\" by setup instructions or scenario effects. An activated Location has no game effect per se, but some scenario effects will reference whether or not a Location is activated."
msgstr ""

msgid "When you are instructed to \"activate\" a Location, place I resource on that Location, which becomes activated."
msgstr ""

msgid "You cannot activate a Location that is already activated."
msgstr ""

msgid "When you are instructed to \"deactivate\" a Location, remove the resource from the Location, which becomes deactivated."
msgstr ""

msgid "You cannot deactivate a Location that is not currently activated."
